<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>software development - Tag - MubarekSD</title><link>https://mubareksd.github.io/tags/software-development/</link><description>software development - Tag - MubarekSD</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>mubareksd@gmail.com (Mubarek Seid Juhar)</managingEditor><webMaster>mubareksd@gmail.com (Mubarek Seid Juhar)</webMaster><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License.</copyright><atom:link href="https://mubareksd.github.io/tags/software-development/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Join the GitHub Student Developer Pack in a few easy steps</title><link>https://mubareksd.github.io/github_student_pack_apply/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 21:29:01 +0800</pubDate><author><name>Mubarek Seid Juhar</name></author><guid>https://mubareksd.github.io/github_student_pack_apply/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/github_student_pack_apply/featured-image.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><p>The GitHub Student Developer Pack is a great way for students to get access to the tools and resources they need to succeed in the tech industry. Applying for the pack is quick and easy, and you can be up and running in no time.</p>
<p><strong>Here are the steps on how to apply for the GitHub Student Developer Pack:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Go to the GitHub Education website. <a href="https://education.github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://education.github.com</a> and click on the &ldquo;Join Global Campus&rdquo; button.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png, /github_student_pack_apply/0.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/0.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/0.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>Click on the &ldquo;Sign up for Student Developer Pack&rdquo; button.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png, /github_student_pack_apply/1.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/1.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/1.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>Click on the &ldquo;Get student benefits&rdquo; button.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png, /github_student_pack_apply/2.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/2.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/2.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>Create a GitHub account or log in to your existing account.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png, /github_student_pack_apply/3.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/3.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/3.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>select your school-issued email address if you have it else choose any email, school name and how are you going to use github. and click &ldquo;continue&rdquo; button.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png, /github_student_pack_apply/4.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/4.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/4.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>If required, upload proof of your student status. and click on &ldquo;Process my application&rdquo; button.
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png" title="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png" data-thumbnail="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Complete configuration preview</h2>">
        <img
            
            loading="lazy"
            src="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png"
            srcset="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png, /github_student_pack_apply/5.png 1.5x, /github_student_pack_apply/5.png 2x"
            sizes="auto"
            alt="/github_student_pack_apply/5.png" height="1562"  width="2450" >
    </a><figcaption class="image-caption">Complete configuration preview</figcaption>
    </figure></li>
<li>Review the terms and conditions and click on the &ldquo;Accept&rdquo; button.</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Once your application is approved, you will receive an email confirmation. You will then be able to access all of the benefits of the GitHub Student Developer Pack.</strong></p>]]></description></item><item><title>GitHub Student Pack: Unlock your developer potential</title><link>https://mubareksd.github.io/github_student_pack/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 21:29:01 +0800</pubDate><author><name>Mubarek Seid Juhar</name></author><guid>https://mubareksd.github.io/github_student_pack/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/github_student_pack/featured-image.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><p>As a student aspiring to make a mark in the tech world, equipping yourself with the right tools and resources is crucial. The GitHub Student Developer Pack is a treasure trove of benefits designed to empower you on your journey to becoming a skilled developer.</p>
<p>With this pack, you gain access to a vast array of free and discounted tools and services from leading companies in the industry. From IDEs and cloud computing platforms to learning resources and developer communities, the pack has everything you need to accelerate your learning and development.</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>